  "markup": "Chronic foot pain, though not deadly is certainly an unpleasant condition to deal with on a daily basis. Often through lack of knowledge of proper foot wear and care, a patient\u0026rsquo;s foot pain will become a chronic condition; and though not often disabling, their life style, activities of daily living, and overall quality of life are profoundly affected. \u003Cbr /\u003E\n\u003Cbr /\u003E\nJoin Dr. Chris Carraway and special guest speaker Dr. Kevin Wong, a respected industry expert as they review aspects of treating the human foot with Low Level Laser, exercise, insoles and various other treatment methods."
}]]></Value>
